graph LR
    ODHController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>OpenshiftNotebookReconciler]

    %% External Dependencies - Upstream
    ODHController -->|watches CRD| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller v1<br/>Provides Notebook CRD]

    %% External Dependencies - OpenShift
    ODHController -->|creates Routes| RouteAPI[OpenShift Route API<br/>route.openshift.io/v1<br/>Required]
    ODHController -->|reads cluster config| ConfigAPI[OpenShift Config API<br/>config.openshift.io/v1<br/>Optional]
    ODHController -->|uses sidecar image| OAuthProxyImage[OpenShift OAuth Proxy<br/>registry.redhat.io/openshift4/ose-oauth-proxy<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies - Kubernetes
    ODHController -->|creates policies| NetworkingAPI[Kubernetes Networking API<br/>networking.k8s.io/v1<br/>Required]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHController -.->|certificate provisioning| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA Operator<br/>Auto-provisions TLS certs]

    %% Integration Points - Control Plane
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server] -->|admission webhook| WebhookService[ODH Webhook Service<br/>/mutate-notebook-v1]
    WebhookService --> ODHController

    %% Integration Points - OpenShift Infrastructure
    IngressController[OpenShift Ingress Controller] -->|provisions URLs| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>Per-notebook external access]
    Routes -.->|created by| ODHController

    ServiceCA -->|injects certs| WebhookCert[Webhook TLS Certificate]
    ServiceCA -->|injects certs| OAuthCert[OAuth Proxy TLS Certificate]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    subgraph NotebookRuntime["Notebook Runtime Dependencies"]
        OAuthSidecar[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>When inject-oauth=true]
        OAuthSidecar -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>SSO Authentication]
        OAuthSidecar -->|authorizes via| SARAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Subject Access Review]
        OAuthSidecar -->|proxies to| JupyterLab[JupyterLab Container<br/>localhost:8888]
    end

    ODHController -.->|injects at creation| OAuthSidecar

    %% Styling
    style ODHController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style RouteAPI fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ConfigAPI fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OAuthProxyImage fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style NetworkingAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style WebhookService fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style IngressController fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Routes fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style WebhookCert fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style OAuthCert fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style OAuthSidecar fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OAuthServer fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SARAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style JupyterLab fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
